::Mosquitor::

Mosquitor yelps in pain as Cyber Claw ramms he feet spikes into his chest. He 
stumbles back, mechfluid dripping onto the floor.

"Leadership!" he yells into his comm-link to Hell Beast, "The base is being 
invaded!"

Mosquitor looks back at Cyber Claw. With an insane battle cry, he pulls out 
his sword stabbing it at his opponent.
